sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as /api/user
    participant Auth
    participant Db as FinancetrackerContext

    Client->>API: GET /api/user
    API->>Auth: validate token -> get userId
    Auth-->>API: userId
    API->>Db: SELECT user WHERE userId
    Db-->>API: user
    API-->>Client: 200 OK { user }
